# Crawler — Layer Definitions
# See CLAUDE.md "Layer Rules" for documentation.

# L0: Foundation / Domain — no internal imports
0 domain
0 frontier
0 config
0 metrics
0 adaptive
0 proxypool
0 coordination
0 queue
0 content/contenttype

# L1: Persistence
1 database
1 storage
1 archive
1 logs

# L2: Content & External I/O
2 content
2 sources
2 feed
2 fetcher
2 scraper
2 discovery
2 leadership
2 render

# L3: Orchestration
3 crawler
3 scheduler
3 job
3 worker
3 events
3 admin

# L4: HTTP
4 api

# Exempt: bootstrap assembles everything
exempt bootstrap

# Known violations (tracked for future cleanup):
# database → discovery: discovery.SourceCandidate types should move to domain/
allow database discovery
